Monaco Vice President Vadim Vasilyev on Lemar: &quot;Thomas wanted to go to #Arsenal &amp; Liverpool. We took a communal decision so he could stay&quot;<br />
<br />
Vasilyev on Lemar: &quot;He is a very important player. We could not have sold him, it would have affected the entire team &amp; the individuals&quot;

Xhaka: &quot;The start against Chelsea was good. Leicester, it was a crazy game. Stoke, we're unhappy we lost, we were clearly the better team.&quot;<br />
<br />
Xhaka: &quot;Against Liverpool, we didn't show up on the pitch. It is not the start we wanted, but there are still 35 laps ahead of us.&quot;
